text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea foraminifera is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family. It is endemic to Borneo.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea foraminifera". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T31918A9668239. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31918A9668239.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
